---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="hero-greeting">Hi, my name is</p>
    <h1 class="hero-name">Hanif Zufar Rafif.</h1>
    <h2 class="hero-tagline">Computer Engineer & AI Application Engineer.</h2>
    <p class="hero-desc">
      I build intelligent automation, scalable AI agents, and robust full-stack applications that bridge backend systems with cutting-edge AI.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="/#projects" class="btn btn-primary">See my work &rarr;</a>
      <a href="/#contact" class="btn btn-outline">Get in touch</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: var(--space-3xl) 0 var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .hero-greeting {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .hero-name {
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    max-width: 660px;
  }

  .hero-desc {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 540px;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
</style>
